WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.050 --> 00:00:00.475
[Forest path, night]

2
00:00:00.575 --> 00:00:04.251
Lin Zhaode (singing): The night is dark,

3
00:00:04.251 --> 00:00:07.131
[Opera orchestra plays]

4
00:00:07.131 --> 00:00:14.427
all is still, and

5
00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:29.525
the moonlight is dim.

6
00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.000
[Sound effect: Bird calls and flapping wings]

7
00:00:36.400 --> 00:00:40.212
The wind is chilly, the shadows are swaying;

8
00:00:40.625 --> 00:00:44.800
a meteorite traces the sky and a strange bird cries out.

9
00:00:44.200 --> 00:00:44.900
[Sound effect: Bird call]

10
00:00:44.925 --> 00:00:49.525
Not even a hint of another person as I

11
00:00:49.875 --> 00:01:19.900
walk alone, which scares me out of my wits.

12
00:01:24.300 --> 00:01:36.325
The gift of money from a beautiful lady is so affectionate,

13
00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:51.250
it makes me feel both ashamed of myself and fond of her.

14
00:01:52.275 --> 00:02:02.850
I see that the garden gate is ajar.

15
00:02:07.175 --> 00:02:20.175
Xuechun must be inside.

16
00:02:20.625 --> 00:02:22.250
[Garden gate]

17
00:02:22.300 --> 00:02:24.300
[Sound effect: Gate creaks open]

18
00:02:25.150 --> 00:02:26.150
Lin Zhaode: Xuechun…
